<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 12:23:32 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>新兴市场投资组合 5 月份外资连续第七个月流入 -IIF</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/emerging/em-portfolios-see-foreign-inflows-seventh-straight-month-may-iif-2024-06-06/</link><description>银行业贸易组织的一份报告显示，由于投资者将资金投入债券，新兴市场五月份连续第七个月吸引了外国投资组合流入，但美国持续高利率正在使前景黯淡。</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 12:05:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/emerging/em-portfolios-see-foreign-inflows-seventh-straight-month-may-iif-2024-06-06/</guid></item><item><title>受到美国审查的制药商员工与中国军事科学家合作</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/staff-drugmaker-under-us-scrutiny-worked-with-chinese-military-scientists-2024-06-06/</link><description>路透社查阅的公开专利记录和科学论文显示，制药商药明康德的员工因与中国军方的联系而受到美国审查，该公司的员工与中国人民解放军的科学家共同发明了高原反应治疗药物。</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 10:36:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/staff-drugmaker-under-us-scrutiny-worked-with-chinese-military-scientists-2024-06-06/</guid></item><item><title>中国蔚来预计第二季度电动汽车销量将增长一倍以上</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-nio-expects-q2-ev-sales-more-than-double-2024-06-06/</link><description>中国电动汽车制造商蔚来汽车周四表示，预计第二季度的交付量将比去年同期增加一倍以上，达到 54,000 辆至 56,000 辆之间。</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 10:36:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-nio-expects-q2-ev-sales-more-than-double-2024-06-06/</guid></item><item><title>早盘出价：英伟达超越苹果、欧洲央行和加拿大央行宽松政策，创下新高</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-06-06/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 10:11:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-06-06/</guid></item><item><title>美国太阳能项目可能会在耗尽免税面板过剩的最后期限内蓬勃发展</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-solar-projects-could-boom-amid-deadline-use-up-tax-exempt-panel-glut-2024-06-06/</link><description>美国对东南亚太阳能电池板的两年关税假期将于周四到期，美国项目开发商开始在今年年底之前使用他们在此期间免税储存的大量设备。</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 10:09:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-solar-projects-could-boom-amid-deadline-use-up-tax-exempt-panel-glut-2024-06-06/</guid></item><item><title>来自世界各地的移民穿越加州沙漠到达美国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/migrants-around-world-traverse-california-desert-reach-us-2024-06-06/</link><description>几个小时前穿过美墨边境的移民家庭靠在边境墙上生锈的钢板条上，在防水布和帐篷下休息，等待边境巡逻人员。</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 10:04:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/migrants-around-world-traverse-california-desert-reach-us-2024-06-06/</guid></item><item><title>梅赛德斯首席执行官预计欧盟很快就会对中国电动汽车关税做出决定</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/mercedes-chief-expects-eu-decision-chinese-evs-tariffs-soon-2024-06-06/</link><description>梅赛德斯奔驰首席执行官奥拉·卡林纽斯 (Ola Kaellenius) 在周四的行业会议上表示，预计欧盟将很快就对中国电动汽车征收的进口关税做出决定。</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 09:45:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/mercedes-chief-expects-eu-decision-chinese-evs-tariffs-soon-2024-06-06/</guid></item><item><title>中国表示从未使用世贸组织禁止的电动汽车补贴</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-says-it-never-uses-ev-subsidies-barred-by-wto-2024-06-06/</link><description>中国外交部发言人周四表示，中国从未利用世界贸易组织禁止的电动汽车补贴。</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 08:14:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-says-it-never-uses-ev-subsidies-barred-by-wto-2024-06-06/</guid></item><item><title>中国表示对与美国的太空合作持开放态度，但“障碍”仍然存在</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/science/china-says-open-space-cooperation-with-us-hurdles-remain-2024-06-06/</link><description>在美国宇航局对中国嫦娥六号月球背面任务表示祝贺后，外交部周四表示，中国对与包括美国在内的国家在太空领域的合作持开放态度。</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 07:54:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/science/china-says-open-space-cooperation-with-us-hurdles-remain-2024-06-06/</guid></item><item><title>美国商业组织表示，两党对台湾的支持给自由贸易协定带来了希望</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/bipartisan-support-taiwan-gives-hope-free-trade-deal-us-business-group-says-2024-06-06/</link><description>台湾美国商会主席周四表示，美国两党对台湾的高度政治支持给最终签署自由贸易协定带来了希望，特别是考虑到当前谈判取得的进展。</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 07:13:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/bipartisan-support-taiwan-gives-hope-free-trade-deal-us-business-group-says-2024-06-06/</guid></item><item><title>受Shein、Temu欢迎的无关税运输遭遇美国海关减速</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/no-tariff-shipments-popular-with-shein-temu-hit-us-customs-speedbump-2024-06-06/</link><description>行业专家表示，美国对处理来自中国相关巨头 Shein 和 Temu 等数十亿美元廉价网购订单的报关行实施新的打击措施，可能会导致交货延误和瓶颈。</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 07:03:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/no-tariff-shipments-popular-with-shein-temu-hit-us-customs-speedbump-2024-06-06/</guid></item><item><title>碧桂园香港清算听证会进一步延期至7月</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/country-gardens-hong-kong-liquidation-hearing-further-adjourned-july-2024-06-06/</link><description>陷入困境的碧桂园在周四提交的一份文件中表示，香港高等法院已将寻求对这家中国房地产开发商进行清算的请愿书的听证会进一步推迟至7月29日。</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 04:51:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/country-gardens-hong-kong-liquidation-hearing-further-adjourned-july-2024-06-06/</guid></item><item><title>美国批准以8000万美元向台湾出售F-16零部件</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-approves-sale-f-16-parts-taiwan-80-mln-2024-06-06/</link><description>五角大楼国防安全合作局周三表示，美国国务院已批准向台湾出售 F-16 战斗机备件和维修零件，价值估计为 8000 万美元。</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 03:56:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-approves-sale-f-16-parts-taiwan-80-mln-2024-06-06/</guid></item><item><title>欧洲央行近五年来首次降息，欧洲股市反弹</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-06-06/</link><description>世界股市正处于历史新高的边缘，欧元周四上涨，此前人们普遍预计欧洲央行将进行近五年来的首次降息。</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 02:32:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-06-06/</guid></item><item><title>外汇 在欧洲央行决定之前欧元保持稳定</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/euro-steadies-ahead-ecb-decision-dollar-dips-2024-06-06/</link><description>欧元周四在欧洲央行政策会议之前保持坚挺，交易员将关注利率制定者对未来政策路径的言论，因为本次会议降息已成定局。</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 01:57:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/euro-steadies-ahead-ecb-decision-dollar-dips-2024-06-06/</guid></item></channel></rss>